{
  "stem": "25639.9",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now in Malmo, we were quarantined.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- in different high schools, and I was in the [? orka ?] skola in Landskrona.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a 25-feet double fence area, beyond which the population could not-- not go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so it seemed that they were very curious about us, and they lined the outer fences to look at us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They learned about us in the newspapers and the radio, at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of these people that came to visit-- later, when I got up, I-- I met some of these people-- and there were actually two families that wanted to adopt me, because once I felt better-- I-- I didn't feel sick, I just felt that I needed to rest and I needed to drink and eat.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, for a whole month, we had nothing but oatmeal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I-- it-- I was very, very emaciated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to know it, but I don't remember anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very, very thin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember, if I may back-- go back a step to Malmo, we were taken to-- to this beautiful high school with an Olympic-sized swimming pool where we showered, received new clothes, and as I mentioned, we were sprayed with DDT first.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it-- these showers-- they were multi-headed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- they were large rooms with shower heads, and we were afraid to go in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were afraid because to us that meant maybe gas will come out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just had a very hard time to get used to normal situations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had to be proven to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somebody yelled, well, how do we know that they're not gas?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they turned the water and after that, we just went in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but there was a full length mirror.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
